            <title>[CASSANDRA-3155] Secondary index should report it&apos;s memory consumption</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3155</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
